      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">VPRS 5887/PO/4, Secretary's outward letter books, p. 586, VA 912 Trustees of the Public Library, Museum and National Gallery of Victoria, Public Record Office, Victoria. ¶ 20th of August [188]8 ¶ edit...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">88.08.20</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Thomas Bride</p>
            <p rend="space"
               style="text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">VPRS 5887/PO/4, Secretary's outward letter books, p. 586, VA 912 Trustees of the Public Library, Museum and National Gallery of Victoria, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">20th of August [188]8<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to acknowledge the receipt of your letter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>addressed to the President of the Trustees<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>George Verdon; l</seg>etter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>suggesting that Mr C Walter should be employed by the Trustees during the Centennial International Exhibition<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Centennial International Exhibition, Melbourne, 1888-9.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to collect specimens for the proposed Botanic Museum,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">The report of the Trustees of the Public Library, Museums, and National Gallery of Victoria, for 1888, referred to this proposal:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0.6666in; text-indent: 0in; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Whenever additional space can be provided it is proposed to give special prominence to the specimens of economic botany, and to rearrange the collections so that information concerning the vegetable products of Australia and their<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>uses may be more easily obtained than<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is now possible. The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Trustees have received valuable suggestions from Baron von Mueller on the details of this change, which will be duly considered when they<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>are able to rearrange the technological collections<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Victoria Parliamentary Paper No. 59, 1889,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>p. 4).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and to inform you that the subject will be brought before the Trustees at their next meeting.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honour to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your Obedient Servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Librarian<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The file copy is not signed.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Ferdinand von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">South Yarra.</p>
         </div>
